description: Data acquired by 3G service from the main computer. The data comes from from 8 differents subsystems, thus 32 light sensors monitoring 2 bandwidths.

targets.rawSql:
SELECT DATE_FORMAT(timeStamp, "%Y-%m-%d %H:%i:%S") AS "timeStamp"
FROM DetectorUnitsData
ORDER BY timeStamp DESC
LIMIT 1;

panels.description: Blue Power in Shrubs for all heights

targets.rawSql:
SELECT
  UNIX_TIMESTAMP(timeStamp) AS "time",
  powerMean AS "Blue irradiance",
  wavelength as metric
FROM PhotodiodeData
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(timeStamp) AND
  location = 'S' AND
  wavelength = '400' AND
  height = "325.00"
ORDER BY timeStamp, height DESC;

SELECT
  UNIX_TIMESTAMP(timeStamp) AS "time",
  powerMean AS "IR irradiance",
  wavelength as metric
FROM PhotodiodeData
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(timeStamp) AND
  location = 'S' AND
  wavelength = '700' AND
  height = "325.00"
ORDER BY timeStamp, height DESC;
